    - **Advice**: "Focus on consistency this month..."
- **Premium Upsell** (if free user): "Unlock detailed 5-year prediction" button at bottom.

## 4. History Screen
**Layout**:
- **List View**: Chronological list of past readings.
    - Thumbnails of the scanned palm.
    - Date & Primary focus (e.g., "Career Reading - Nov 22").
- **Filter**: Dropdown to filter by "Love", "Career", "General".
- **Search**: Search bar for keywords in past readings.

## 5. Profile Screen
**Layout**:
- **Personal Details**: Name, DOB (crucial for horoscope), Gender.
- **Subscription Status**:
    - "Free Member" -> "Upgrade to Sage Premium".
- **Settings**:
    - Notification preferences (Daily Horoscope).
    - "Delete My Data" (Privacy compliance).
- **Support**: Help Center, Rate App.
